title: Stunning 3BR 2Bath Penthouse Condo- private 2car garage
map_address: N Western Ave near W Le Moyne St
posting_body: ['Spacious Penthouse occupies entire extra wide 2nd story in boutique elevator building.', "Elevator opens into unit's mudroom.", 'Minutes walk to blue line, 606 , downtown Wicker Park/Bucktown, Logan/Palmer Square.', 'Video security system for building.', 'Additional security system in unit.', '3 large private decks + shared rooftop deck.', 'Custom drapes, gas fireplace, gourmet kitchen, granite counter tops, SS appliances, 52 bottle wine fridge.', "Hardwood oak floors throughout; 11' ceilings w/ custom crown molding.", 'Master BR includes wall-to-wall windows w/ custom drapes, 2 custom closets w/ built-ins, walk out to private deck.', 'Master BA just renovated w brand new freestanding tub, heated floor, separate mosaic tiled steam shower w/ multiple shower heads.', 'Large 2nd and 3rd BRs- both with separate private decks, built-in closets, Large 2nd BA w/ mosaic tiled Jacuzzi tub/shower.', 'In Unit W/D. RARE 2 car attached/secure/private Garage parking incl with additional gated private drive into garage.', 'This apartment is truly immaculate w unique finishes throughout.', 'Very rare secured 2 car garage.', 'Rented to same tenant for past 4+ years.', 'The neighbors are wonderful.', 'The location is beyond convenient.', 'Blue line, coffee, grocer, fitness, bars, restaurants and shops all within blocks.', 'Only 5 min drive to expressways (90/94/290).']
